        { "kind": "paragraph", "runs": [{ "kind": "text", "value": "Red, Blue and Green laboratories are inspected on Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday, one per day. Red is not inspected on Monday. Blue is inspected before Red. Green is inspected on Wednesday. When is Red inspected?" }] }
